  "detailed_description": "In The Steps as we know them, you use the moves of chess to find your way through different worlds. It is a puzzle game with a relaxing atmosphere. The game has simple mechanics, but is challenging at the same time.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573800/extras/c1a9eaf5784b7de9f0648e823ded775b.poster.avif?t=1622484625\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573800/extras/c1a9eaf5784b7de9f0648e823ded775b.webm?t=1622484625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573800/extras/c1a9eaf5784b7de9f0648e823ded775b.mp4?t=1622484625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Different situations</h2><br>Every world you come across uses a different chess piece and brings a different tactic with it. The levels build up from the easy moves of a pawn to the difficult situations of a knight. Sometimes you can work your way through by being stubborn. In other levels you have to take a step back and take a second look.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573800/extras/86ee777418cb602a621759f4f7b31384.avif?t=1622484625\" width=600 height=150 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The game</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>6 worlds<br></li><li>6 different chess pieces<br></li><li>~7 levels per world<br></li><li>From easy to complicated</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573800/extras/c5d83cf2a27a14b2f73498649ac3e897.poster.avif?t=1622484625\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573800/extras/c5d83cf2a27a14b2f73498649ac3e897.webm?t=1622484625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1573800/extras/c5d83cf2a27a14b2f73498649ac3e897.mp4?t=1622484625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
